Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:13.44,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Well aren’t you having fun!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.52,0:01:00.95,Kaho,,0,0,0,,School Idol Connect…?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:03.06,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wait, you mean SIC?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:23.46,Kaho,,0,0,0,,A video?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:25.35,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Not a stream?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:17.61,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We aren’t losing to you!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.85,0:02:23.65,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Rurino-chan! You don’t need to be rude!!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.91,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Alright, that should be… it!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:49.25,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Does it look right?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.75,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah…\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:20.30,Kaho,,0,0,0,,The difference between videos and streams…\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.20,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I don’t think I’ve ever really thought about it before.\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:33.23,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And it’s Rurino-chan’s first school festival, too…\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.78,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Have fun, Sayaka-chan!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:06.78,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Right, Acting Leader?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.69,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chaaan, don’t forget to smile!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.32,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Aaand cut!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:20.80,Kaho,,0,0,0,,The way you said everything so neatly was really cool, Sayaka-chan!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:23.01,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I think that was great!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:42.33,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hi everyone! I’m Hinoshita Kaho, a first-year from the Hasunosora School Idol Club!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:44.63,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hi e-very-one~?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.48,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah, ‘afternoon!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:56.63,Kaho,,0,0,0,,All of us are really working hard with our Rindou Festival coming up, buuut!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:06:03.75,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Now that I’ve been a school idol for half a year, it’s time to take on Love Live!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:07.99,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I hear there’s a looot of school idols that are gonna be competing in the qualifiers, so…\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:16.07,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Since we’re gonna be one of those groups, we’re gonna have to show off what makes us so charming!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:18.45,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Looks like this is gonna be very, very hard!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:22.18,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But that’s exactly why I wanna blossom!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:31.15,Kaho,,0,0,0,,The Rindou Festival we’ll be using as our stage is an important tradition here at Hasunosora, so we wanna do as much as we can!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:34.37,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We hope you’ll come and support us!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:40.50,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…How was that?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:56.35,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yay!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:59.86,Kaho,,0,0,0,,So you’re the only one left, Rurino-chan. Think you can do it?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:34.37,Kaho,,0,0,0,,She’s motivated, but not in a good way!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.49,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You’ve got this~!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:28.90,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Perfeeeect!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:36.46,Kaho,,0,0,0,,That was really good!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.84,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You’re doing it because it seems fun!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.28,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Let’s rub it in that student council president’s face!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:21.79,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Besides, is that really something you can learn just by watching her!?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.79,Kaho,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:26.52,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Grrrr…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.51,Rurino,,0,0,0,,There’s something I want even more than that right now…!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:56.05,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But it’s thanks to a certain someone’s “tests” that we’re in this situation in the first place!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:20.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,We’ll show you, jerk!!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:59.53,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let’s get to recording~!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:04.01,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Well, as much as I’d like to say that…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:11.26,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Maaan… It’s just this whole advertising thing, y’know?\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:14.71,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I dunno what I should say!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:51.39,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Oh, that’d be really helpful!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:54.31,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Very very thank you! You’re welcome!{\i0}\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.86,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Wow…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:06.91,Rurino,,0,0,0,,All I could think of was how cool you two were…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:11.72,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I couldn’t think of anything for the video, but I’m feeling more encouraged now!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.69,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I guess so!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:28.56,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Alright, let’s give it a shot!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:31.52,Rurino,,0,0,0,,If I mess up, we can just do it over!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:40.26,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ah… um…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:43.21,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m School Idol– wait no!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:49.97,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m Osawa Rurino, a first-year in the Hasunosora School Idol Club!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:54.23,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…And… uh…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:08:01.74,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Shoot, I’m not bad with words or anything, but I’m drawing a blank right now!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:09.73,Rurino,,0,0,0,,A-Ahaha, okay, okay!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:13.83,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Right, Kaho-chan and Sayaka-chan are here for me!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:18.58,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve just gotta act natural and say my thoughts about the Rindou Festival!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:22.18,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Cogito, ergo Ruri.\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:23.68,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:30.50,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I can’t really say anything special to promote ourselves, but hm…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:36.08,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Mira-Cra Park! will definitely be performing on stage!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:39.21,Rurino,,0,0,0,,We’ll definitely get that permission!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:44.39,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And… I’m gonna help Megu-chan get her revenge!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:50.57,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And… about the Love Live! qualifiers, huh…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:56.24,Rurino,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I still don’t get the whole school idol thing.\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:09:03.73,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I still don’t really know how I’m supposed to feel about competing in Love Live!, either…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:08.08,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Hm…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:13.44,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Sorry, all I could think about has to do with Megu-chan.\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:20.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I probably don’t even know one percent of the fun that goes into being a school idol.\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:22.98,Rurino,,0,0,0,,We probably ought to cut this out and re-record–\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.52,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Oh, I see.\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:32.51,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I-I think I figured it out!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:39.47,Rurino,,0,0,0,,That time I watched Megu-chan editing videos, I remember I wanted to give it a go!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:42.59,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So it’s like…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:45.25,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I really like fun stuff!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:51.11,Rurino,,0,0,0,,When I was thinking how I’d want to tweak the video, I was really excited to see how much fun it’d be!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:54.33,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I guess school idols are kinda like that!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:10:03.33,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Maybe it’s not good for me to have Megu-chan as my only reason, but I can’t lie to myself!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.02,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I wanna be there for Megu-chan’s revenge!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:13.77,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Right now, whenever I see the fun stuff Megu-chan does, it makes me wanna try a bunch of stuff out too!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:16.02,Rurino,,0,0,0,,That’s how I feel about Love Live!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,If it’ll be fun, then I’m gonna do it!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:22.29,Rurino,,0,0,0,,That’s how I’ve always done things!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:27.01,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And that’s exactly why I wanna perform in Love Live!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.29,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Whoa, really!?\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:48.01,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Oh! Yeah, yeah, I did!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:51.90,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Looks like that still hasn’t changed!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.28,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Aw, yeah!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:11.51,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Hehe, maybe I’ll pull a Megu-chan and throw a lil’ edit together…!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:10.90,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Time for your second test, challengers…!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:15.26,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Ahaha!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:20.52,Sachi,,0,0,0,,If you want your venue, you’re gonna have to go through me!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:23.73,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Now, pass my tests!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:31.59,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Oh? Are you going to devour me now?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:33.49,Sachi,,0,0,0,,And how will that help you pass the tests???\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.99,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Um, you need your box?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:42.23,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Heh, right.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:47.79,Sachi,,0,0,0,,You all seem pretty motivated right now, huh…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:51.81,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Alright then! I will unveil the test now!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:55.98,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Your second test is…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:57.94,Sachi,,0,0,0,,School Idol Connect!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:11.39,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Right. It’s the same one you always use.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:14.85,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Oh, you always use it, hm… Not bad…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:21.46,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Your test is to use that same app, and upload a video advertising the Hasunosora School Idol Club!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:30.00,Sachi,,0,0,0,,The benefit of a video is the ability to convey your points in a short amount of time.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:36.90,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Unlike a livestream, you have to think about what you want to say and how to sway people’s hearts to your cause.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:44.87,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Bwahahaha! How’s that!?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:48.85,Sachi,,0,0,0,,You agree that you need to get yourselves out there before the Rindou Festival, don’t you?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.00,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Good luck!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.88,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Na–hahaha!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:01.25,Sachi,,0,0,0,,If you’re mad about it, get to it then!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:08.14,Sachi,,0,0,0,,If your performance at the festival isn’t exciting, then there’s no way you’ll get past the Love Live! qualifiers!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:32.39,Sachi,,0,0,0,,…Heh.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.99,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Guess I should get to work too~\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:07.66,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If we’re talking about the same SIC, then it’s where we upload our livestreams.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:41.42,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Despite the villainous phrasing, that’s something entirely proper…!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:11.08,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,U-Understood…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.16,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If that’s what you want, we’ll do it.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:51.84,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yes, this should be perfect.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:56.04,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If we set the phone here, it should be good.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:05.57,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Rurino-san?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:28.96,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,And when we record videos of our performances, there’s no need to really think about it since that’s all we’re recording.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:38.00,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Why don’t we start with Kaho-san and me, then?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:41.77,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I think I know what I want to say.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:49.02,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Of course, Kaho-san is free to agree or disagree, but I think having Rurino-san go last will help her come up with something.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:57.78,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Shouldn’t I be the one saying that…?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:01.77,Sayaka,,0,0,0,, A-Anyway, we should decide who goes first–\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:11.10,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…Somehow I knew this would happen!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.20,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:21.66,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I am Murano Sayaka, a first-year in the Hasunosora School Idol Club.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:30.72,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Today, I have some announcements regarding our \Nperformance in our school’s upcoming Rindou Festival.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:35.52,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,O-Okay…!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:39.05,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,With the addition of Mira-Cra Park!,\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:43.97,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,our upcoming performance will have all three subunits performing in it, so we hope to see you all there.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:50.72,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Of note in this performance is the opportunity to unveil our full, six-member School Idol Club–\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:57.92,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,And of course, our motivation as we look toward the upcoming Love Live! qualifiers.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:04.75,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,As a school idol myself, I am looking forward to performing in the competition!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.87,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,How was that, I wonder…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:13.71,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I don’t think I said anything wrong, but…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.76,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,P-Phew…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:28.36,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Okay, let’s switch places now.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.34,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh, you want me to respond!?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.95,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,G-Good afternoon…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.74,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I thought it was amazing!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.57,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That’s right…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:53.72,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,While we are using it for our Love Live! entry, the Rindou Festival is still an important tradition…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:17.62,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,There’s no need to worry, Rurino-san.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.76,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,We can re-record as many times as we have to.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.81,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.14,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Rurino-san?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:39.11,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You’ll do it because it seems fun…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:44.57,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You said the same thing back when you first joined the club, right?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:54.78,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Hehe, seems so.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:58.14,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I think that’s a very charming part of you.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:17.29,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I don’t think Megumi-senpai edits like that, though…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
